                    <h2>Object Association: Aggregation (<code>HAS-A</code>) vs Composition</h2>
                    <p>In <strong>Aggregation</strong> (<code>HAS-A</code>), one class contains a pointer/reference to another class (<code>Department</code> has <code>Professor*</code>), but if the container dies, the contained object lives on independently.</p>
